OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780146665
OL,3,CMan hospitalised after falling on boat
OL,4,Coff the coast of Alderney
OL,6,FA man has been airlifted to hospital
OL,7,Fafter falling on a yacht and
OL,8,Fsustaining significant injuries off
OL,9,Fthe coast of Alderney on Friday.
OL,11,FThe Alderney All Weather Lifeboat and
OL,12,Fthe French Maritime Rescue
OL,13,FCoordination Centre responded to a
OL,14,Fdistress call from a yacht just before
OL,15,Fmidday.
OL,17,FParamedics treated the casualty
OL,18,Fonboard and less than two hours after
OL,19,Fthe call out he was flown to Guernsey
OL,20,Fto be taken to hospital by Coastguard
OL,21,FOfficers.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
