FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780146665
OL,3,CMan hospitalised after falling on boat
OL,4,Coff the coast of Alderney
OL,6,FHe is believed to be in a stable
OL,7,Fcondition but admitted for further
OL,8,Fchecks.
OL,10,FHowever, it wasn't the only emergency
OL,11,Fon Friday. The coastguard received
OL,12,Fmultiple distress calls including
OL,13,Freports of a missing person, someone
OL,14,Fcaught in flooding tides and a broken
OL,15,Fdown vessel.
OL,17,FAll calls were attended to and
OL,18,Fresolved on the day.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
