FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780146665
OL,3,CMan hospitalised after falling on boat
OL,4,Coff the coast of Alderney
OL,6,FDuty Search and Rescue Mission
OL,7,FCoordinator, Simon Granger says: "This
OL,8,Fwas a busy afternoon which involved
OL,9,Fnumerous emergency response agencies
OL,10,Ffrom Guernsey, Alderney and France,
OL,11,Fand is a credit to the strong working
OL,12,Frelationships between the neighbouring
OL,13,Frescue services.
OL,15,F"Following receipt of the distress
OL,16,Fcall, Coastguard Officers in Guernsey
OL,17,Fquickly identified the seriousness of
OL,18,Fthe situation and coordinated the
OL,19,Fdeployment of the most appropriate
OL,20,Frescue assets to the scene.
OL,26,@oD@bOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780146665
OL,3,CMan hospitalised after falling on boat
OL,4,Coff the coast of Alderney
OL,6,F"The response was further assisted by
OL,7,Fa nearby vessel answering the Mayday
OL,8,FRelay and recovering the casualty,
OL,9,Fwhich significantly reduced the time
OL,10,Ftaken to get the patient closer to
OL,11,Fhospital care.
OL,13,F"This coordinated multi-agency
OL,14,Fresponse ensured the casualty reached
OL,15,Fhospital care in the quickest possible
OL,16,Ftimeframe."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@KO]
